properties.Name: OdorQualityType
properties.Description:
The character of an odor is a critical element in assessing an odor. This property is the ability to distinguish different odors and is only descriptive.   This method is most commonly used to define the character of an odor which can then be compared to other odors

Ex:
- Chemical Smell
- Petroleum Smell
- Acidic Smell

Columns.Name: OdorQualityTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an odor quality type.

Columns.Name: OdorQualityTypeName
Columns.Description: The name of an odor quality type.

Columns.Name: OdorQualityTypeDescription
Columns.Description: The description of an odor quality type.
